message.text:
“𝑨𝒏𝒅 𝒊𝒏 𝒕𝒉𝒆 𝒆𝒏𝒅, 𝒊𝒕'𝒔 𝒏𝒐𝒕 𝒕𝒉𝒆 𝒚𝒆𝒂𝒓𝒔 𝒊𝒏 𝒚𝒐𝒖𝒓 𝒍𝒊𝒇𝒆 𝒕𝒉𝒂𝒕 𝒄𝒐𝒖𝒏𝒕. 𝑰𝒕'𝒔 𝒕𝒉𝒆 𝒍𝒊𝒇𝒆 𝒊𝒏 𝒚𝒐𝒖𝒓 𝒚𝒆𝒂𝒓𝒔.” —𝑨𝒃𝒓𝒂𝒉𝒂𝒎 𝑳𝒊𝒏𝒄𝒐𝒍𝒏

PATA Philippines FEU Student Chapter extends their warmest birthday wishes to our remarkable 𝐈𝐓𝐇𝐌 𝐃𝐞𝐚𝐧, 𝐃𝐫. 𝐇𝐚𝐫𝐨𝐥𝐝 𝐁. 𝐁𝐮𝐞𝐧𝐨!

Today, we celebrate not just an esteemed leader, but a visionary and a mentor whose commitment continues to shape the future of our institution in the most profound ways. We are immensely grateful for your unwavering support to students and faculty as well as your tireless dedication to academic excellence. 

May this year bring you continued success, good health, prosperity, and the same positivity that you share with all of us everyday. 

Here's to many more years of excellence and achievements! Happiest birthday, Dean! 💙

Caption by: Jea Madronio
Pubmat by: Vince Maligang

message.text:
“𝑨𝒏𝒅 𝒊𝒏 𝒕𝒉𝒆 𝒆𝒏𝒅, 𝒊𝒕'𝒔 𝒏𝒐𝒕 𝒕𝒉𝒆 𝒚𝒆𝒂𝒓𝒔 𝒊𝒏 𝒚𝒐𝒖𝒓 𝒍𝒊𝒇𝒆 𝒕𝒉𝒂𝒕 𝒄𝒐𝒖𝒏𝒕. 𝑰𝒕'𝒔 𝒕𝒉𝒆 𝒍𝒊𝒇𝒆 𝒊𝒏 𝒚𝒐𝒖𝒓 𝒚𝒆𝒂𝒓𝒔.” —𝑨𝒃𝒓𝒂𝒉𝒂𝒎 𝑳𝒊𝒏𝒄𝒐𝒍𝒏

PATA Philippines FEU Student Chapter extends their warmest birthday wishes to our remarkable 𝐈𝐓𝐇𝐌 𝐃𝐞𝐚𝐧, 𝐃𝐫. 𝐇𝐚𝐫𝐨𝐥𝐝 𝐁. 𝐁𝐮𝐞𝐧𝐨!

Today, we celebrate not just an esteemed leader, but a visionary and a mentor whose commitment continues to shape the future of our institution in the most profound ways. We are immensely grateful for your unwavering support to students and faculty as well as your tireless dedication to academic excellence. 

May this year bring you continued success, good health, prosperity, and the same positivity that you share with all of us everyday. 

Here's to many more years of excellence and achievements! Happiest birthday, Dean! 💙

Caption by: Jea Madronio
Pubmat by: Vince Maligang

“𝑨𝒏𝒅 𝒊𝒏 𝒕𝒉𝒆 𝒆𝒏𝒅, 𝒊𝒕'𝒔 𝒏𝒐𝒕 𝒕𝒉𝒆 𝒚𝒆𝒂𝒓𝒔 𝒊𝒏 𝒚𝒐𝒖𝒓 𝒍𝒊𝒇𝒆 𝒕𝒉𝒂𝒕 𝒄𝒐𝒖𝒏𝒕. 𝑰𝒕'𝒔 𝒕𝒉𝒆 𝒍𝒊𝒇𝒆 𝒊𝒏 𝒚𝒐𝒖𝒓 𝒚𝒆𝒂𝒓𝒔.” —𝑨𝒃𝒓𝒂𝒉𝒂𝒎 𝑳𝒊𝒏𝒄𝒐𝒍𝒏

PATA Philippines FEU Student Chapter extends their warmest birthday wishes to our remarkable 𝐈𝐓𝐇𝐌 𝐃𝐞𝐚𝐧, 𝐃𝐫. 𝐇𝐚𝐫𝐨𝐥𝐝 𝐁. 𝐁𝐮𝐞𝐧𝐨!

Today, we celebrate not just an esteemed leader, but a visionary and a mentor whose commitment continues to shape the future of our institution in the most profound ways. We are immensely grateful for your unwavering support to students and faculty as well as your tireless dedication to academic excellence. 

May this year bring you continued success, good health, prosperity, and the same positivity that you share with all of us everyday. 

Here's to many more years of excellence and achievements! Happiest birthday, Dean! 💙

Caption by: Jea Madronio
Pubmat by: Vince Maligang

“𝑨𝒏𝒅 𝒊𝒏 𝒕𝒉𝒆 𝒆𝒏𝒅, 𝒊𝒕'𝒔 𝒏𝒐𝒕 𝒕𝒉𝒆 𝒚𝒆𝒂𝒓𝒔 𝒊𝒏 𝒚𝒐𝒖𝒓 𝒍𝒊𝒇𝒆 𝒕𝒉𝒂𝒕 𝒄𝒐𝒖𝒏𝒕. 𝑰𝒕'𝒔 𝒕𝒉𝒆 𝒍𝒊𝒇𝒆 𝒊𝒏 𝒚𝒐𝒖𝒓 𝒚𝒆𝒂𝒓𝒔.” —𝑨𝒃𝒓𝒂𝒉𝒂𝒎 𝑳𝒊𝒏𝒄𝒐𝒍𝒏

PATA Philippines FEU Student Chapter extends their warmest birthday wishes to our remarkable 𝐈𝐓𝐇𝐌 𝐃𝐞𝐚𝐧, 𝐃𝐫. 𝐇𝐚𝐫𝐨𝐥𝐝 𝐁. 𝐁𝐮𝐞𝐧𝐨!

Today, we celebrate not just an esteemed leader, but a visionary and a mentor whose commitment continues to shape the future of our institution in the most profound ways. We are immensely grateful for your unwavering support to students and faculty as well as your tireless dedication to academic excellence. 

May this year bring you continued success, good health, prosperity, and the same positivity that you share with all of us everyday. 

Here's to many more years of excellence and achievements! Happiest birthday, Dean! 💙

Caption by: Jea Madronio
Pubmat by: Vince Maligang
